databaseoperation.name: getSubProducer
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select (prdcr_first_name + ' ' + prdcr_last_name) as person_name_ss_filter from person where person_id=#person_id#

databaseoperation.name: getRegistrationTypeIdForAgentOnboaridng
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select master_lookup_data_id as selected_agency_registration_type_id from master_lookup_data_lku where master_lookup_data_desc ='Producer Registration' and master_lookup_detail_id in (select top 1 master_lookup_detail_id from master_lookup_detail_lku where lookup_table_name ='agency_registration_type_lku')

databaseoperation.name: getAgentChecked
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select contacttype from person where LOGIN_ID=#user_id#

databaseoperation.name: getAddressshowdetailMailingType1
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select top 1 state_id,country_code,territory_id from address where agency_id=#agency_id# and type=#type# and person_id is null

databaseoperation.name: getWorkflowStatusByDescription
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: select invitation_status_id as audit_status_id from tbl_invitation_status_lku where [group]='Audit' and [description]='Audit Initiated'
